{"tid":775370,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球王比利睇好利物浦捧英超","createTime":"2018-08-11T06:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T09:21:44.000Z","uid":31314,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"45e1e8e0593dc87f1b3285fe5907fa7e210bac9a","tid":775370,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:13:27.000Z","msg":"新一季英超戰火重燃，當中今夏積極增兵的利物浦被認為是爭標熱門之一，球王比利更睇中他們將贏得冠軍，<br />\n<br />\n紅軍今夏先後買入基達、艾利臣比加及沙基利等新兵，成為英超今夏花費最多的球隊，因此獲得比利睇好有望成為冠軍得主。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>比利</strong></span>在Twitter力撐巴西同鄉費明奴及艾利臣比加說︰「英超今日正式展開，你們認為哪隊會捧盃？<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我覺得今年是屬於利物浦、艾利臣和費明奴。</strong></span>」<br />\n<br />\nIt's the start of the @PremierLeague today. Who do you think will win? <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>I think it's the year of Liverpool, Alisson and Firmino!</strong></span> // &Eacute; o in&iacute;cio da Premier League hoje. Quem voc&ecirc; pensa que vai vencer? Eu acho que este &eacute; o ano do @LFC , com @Alissonbecker e Firmino! <a href=\"https://t.co/59koCXIIqP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F59koCXIIqP&d=XeCWZUIeOedHUKMSG4OZTwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a67b2d56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/59koCXIIqP</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Pel&eacute; (@Pele) August 10, 2018<br />\n不過比利的「烏鴉口」往績人所共知，經典例子包括曾預言非洲球隊可在2000年前贏得世界盃，以及在2002世盃看好阿根廷及法國打入決賽，但最終兩隊在分組賽出局。如今比利力撐紅軍，不知一眾利迷會有何感覺。"},{"pid":"8d5e980cc73b5f405f109ab37b7f98cf62f77961","tid":775370,"uid":15846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:14:50.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1f535a23e6489e728defe19e7e92a02f1b6a44","tid":775370,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:15:02.000Z","msg":"屌 鏝又出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd7364803aa3195e8a24f09f3672fd925b3dc8b","tid":775370,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislik